ys to the $D^+D^-$ pair is\nshown to be incomplete. This constitutes evidence for a new contribution to the\ndecay, potentially one or more new charm-strange resonances in the $D^-K^+$\nchannel with masses around 2.9 GeV$/c^2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2020 18:00:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Sep 2020 13:43:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Dec 2020 16:34:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-18"}
