 erasure correcting codes among others. IMPACT will provide near-real-time\nlocalization of SGRBs with a total delay of $\\sim$5 s, and will enable SONG\ntelescopes to join the efforts to pursue multi-messenger astronomy and help\ndecipher the underlying physics of these events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2020 19:50:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
