 thus in-cluster mergers cannot be ruled out at a\nsignificant level of confidence. A more substantial catalogue of BHB mergers\nand a more extensive library of N-body simulations are needed to constrain the\norigin of the observed events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2020 01:53:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-21"}
