laws on the resolvent of $Y_tY_t^\\top$. These\nresults can be of independent interest, and used as useful inputs for many\nother problems regarding the spectral statistics of $Y_t$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2020 12:44:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 May 2022 17:44:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-25"}
