arned from end-users, and (2) how the evaluation methodology helped the\nbuilders to understand workflows and the effectiveness of their systems. Our\nfindings suggest new insights explaining future design opportunities in the\nAutoML domain as well as how using our methodology helped the builders to\ndetermine insights and let them draw concrete directions for improving their\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2020 14:09:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
